rows.label: qst200602_msg0002
rows.name:
You mean the big monster thing
I saw that one time?

rows.label: qst200602_msg0003
rows.name:
Looked like a pretty nasty
piece of work, that one did.

rows.label: qst200602_msg0004
rows.name:
Actually, it was so out there that
nobody believes me when I tell 'em.

rows.label: qst200602_msg0005
rows.name:
It was early morning when I saw it.
5 o'clock or thereabouts.

rows.label: qst200602_msg0006
rows.name:
Over on the hill near Triedge Isle,
there was this crazy huge shadowy
thing moving about.

rows.label: qst200602_msg0007
rows.name:
Honestly, I thought I was seeing things
too at first. Some kind of bad dream.

rows.label: qst200602_msg0008
rows.name:
I've never heard of any monster
reaching that kind of size.

rows.label: qst200602_msg0009
rows.name:
At any rate, if you're gonna check
it out, you should be careful.

rows.label: qst200602_msg0010
rows.name:
I don't know if even a Divine Beast battleship
would be able to down that behemoth!
